				<p n="11">
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Furens uero Adrianus imperator iussit afferri craticulam, et subter poni flammam ignis ualidam nimis, ita ut craticula similis fieret igni, et sic sanctam Dei uirginem proieceret super eam.</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Spes uero non curabat ignis incendia, sed requiescebat in craticula tanquam nauis in tranquillitate maris, non illi appropinquantibus undis.</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Exclamatur autem uoce magna dicens, “Domine Iesu Christe respice ancillam tuam, et ne facias minui terrores ignis, ut possim resistere aduersus machinationes tiranni istius, et dissolue eius temporalem uirtutem.”</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Transactis autem horarum trium spatiis, ignis non tetigit eam.</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Adrianus uero imperator iussit tolli eam a craticula et poni in sartaginem, et praecepit picem, ceram, et bitumen in unum commisceri, ut feruor intolerabilis de sartagine ascenderet.</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Spes autem respiciens in caelum, et inuocans omnium saluatorem, proiecit se in sataginem, et sic super eam requiescebat, quasi in rore de caelo descendente.</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
