					</s>
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Audiens beata Spes terminum aduersus se a rege difinitum, gaudens deprecabatur matrem suam ut oraret, ut imminentem sibi prospectum efficaciter consequeretur, dicebatque sororibus suis, </lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
