							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Ego enim sorores meae quia uado uiam quam Dominus donare dignatus est, hortor ut et uos in illam inuiolate ingrediamini.</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">De cetero dulcissime sorores, rogo per uestigia mea gradiamini, et honoretis in ea fraternitatis cognitionem, ut bona et maxima promissione pariter perfruamur in regno caelorum.”</lem>
							<rdg wit="#Translation"></rdg>
						</app>
					</s>
				</p>
				<p n="13">
					<s>
						<app>
							<lem wit="#Transcription">Et haec dicens, conplexa est matrem suam et osculata est eam, et postulans orauit, gaudebat autem et exultabat in Domino.</lem>
